Commit Message: There will be application, request and response

Further improved JSON support

Allow iverriding both encoder and decoder.

Better resource endpoint registration

There is no point in registering endpoints for all methods found in
resource object, it's still the same resource.
Less in local storage, better annotations
Allow specifying endpoint name in resource object
Do not use local and local_manager at all
Remove Polls example, superseded by Todos
Remove Click from requirements, it's not yet used
User select done, now user create
Properly pass props and state to render() method

All missing tests

And some unreachable code removed.

General update

* new ReST linter
* removed unused dev packages from setup.py
* adapted to Werkzeug 1.0
* updated Preact in examples
Dummy release to test CodeQL analysis
Run PyPI deployment only if there's no security issues
